OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Ffor a time this evening, with
OL,7,Ftemperatures quickly falling perhaps
OL,8,Fallowing a light grass frost in
OL,9,Fplaces. Then cloud increases with a
OL,10,Ffew showers possibly arriving, before
OL,11,Frain reaches the Derbyshire hills
OL,12,Ftowards dawn. Also becoming breezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FRain quickly spreads east to
OL,15,Fremaining areas, then eases to turn
OL,16,Flight and patchy by late morning, with
OL,17,Fmost places becoming dry and cloudy
OL,18,Fthrough the afternoon. Breezy and mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
