OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBreezy
OL,6,FMonday with rain spreading east but
OL,7,Falso some drier spells. Cloudy Tuesday
OL,8,Fand Wednesday with light winds and
OL,9,Fscattered showers, also some drier
OL,10,Fbrighter interludes. Temperatures
OL,11,Fgenerally near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
